When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi002subs"

When I click tab "Request params" in floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi002subs"
Then I should NOT see floating panel has Params - row "2" - value "jitapi002_id","String".
When I click tab "Response params" in floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi002subs"
Then I should NOT see floating panel has Params - row "6" - value "jitapi002_id","Column Definition","jitapi002_id"
When I close the floating panel
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
When I drag the table Name "jitapi002sub" to new location with x: "200", y: "0"
When I trigger relation popup established from table Name "jitapi002" to table Name "jitapi002sub"
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see the realtion path display
When I navigate to menu "API" without submenu
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitapi002subs" from list
When I wait query data API "jitapi002subs.jitapi002_id" is fetched completely
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi002subs"
When I click tab "SQL Query" in floating panel

When I click tab "Response params" in floating panel
